Package edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_scheduler.course

Class Activity

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc216.wolf_scheduler.course.Activity
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Course, Event
    public abstract class Activity
extends java.lang.Object
    The activity class is an abstract class representing an activity, is parent for both Course and Event, and maintains information for the title, meeting days, and meeting times for an activity
